          "description": "WORST HOSPITAL experience ever! the gyno that I saw had extremely bad bedside manner, made me feel very uncomfortable. the billing is by far the most confusing thing ever - every doctor visit comes with two separate billing statement, from the facility (ny presp) and doctor (weill cornell), and the costs are over the top even with insurance. I\u2019ve been trying to reach the doctors billing department, left multiple messages to sort out bill but still no response, it\u2019s been several months at this point. DONT go here!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURxZ1ByQy1BRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x53a08b3e549cc6a0!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDqgPrC-AE%7C%7C?hl=en",
