          "description": "The hospital staff is ridiculously rude. They don\u2019t help patients they are concerned with not getting a lawsuit. There is a lack of communication with the entire staff due to the doctors, nurses, and security. They aren\u2019t here for safety they are here for protection of themselves. Do not go to this hospital. There are plenty of local hospitals who take care of people better.",
